fields.name: Football
fields.description: A team sport played between two teams of eleven players with a spherical ball.

fields.name: Basketball
fields.description: A team sport in which two teams, most commonly of five players each, oppose each other on a rectangular court.

fields.name: wrestling
fields.description: A racket sport that can be played individually against a single opponent or between two teams of two players each.

fields.name: Volleyball
fields.description: A team sport in which two teams of six players are separated by a net.

fields.name: Rugby
fields.description: A team sport played with an oval-shaped ball by two teams of 15 players.
